 * Jen Processor v6.3 - PER-SESSION ROUTING + EVIDENCE TRACKING
 *
 * v6.3 FIXES:
 * - Process each session independently (no more "first cwd wins")
 * - extractCwdFromContent returns LAST cwd (most accurate)
 * - project_id only used as UUID fallback, not as path
 * - Claude prompt requires 2 context anchors for todos/bugs
 * - All inserts include fingerprint_hash, evidence_excerpt, evidence_refs
 * - Structure entries track operations (add/move/rename/remove)
 */

